# Plugin System

## plugin.manifest.json

- **Wajib**: `id`, `name`, `version`, `description`, `type` (`core-plugin` | `segment-plugin` | `company-plugin`), `dependencies`, `exports`, `permissions`, `routes` (opsional).
- **exports**: `components`, `services`, `screens` (nama route → nama component), `tabs`, `widgets` sesuai kebutuhan.
- **routes**: Array of `{ name, path, component, permissions, meta?: { title, showInMenu?, icon? } }`. `component` harus string nama component yang di-export.

Contoh (snippet):

```json
{
  "id": "payment",
  "type": "core-plugin",
  "dependencies": ["balance"],
  "exports": {
    "components": ["TopUpScreen", "QrScreen"],
    "services": ["paymentService", "topUpService"],
    "screens": { "TopUp": "TopUpScreen", "Qr": "QrScreen" }
  },
  "routes": [
    { "name": "TopUp", "path": "/payment/topup", "component": "TopUpScreen", "permissions": ["payment:topup"], "meta": { "title": "Top Up", "showInMenu": true } }
  ],
  "permissions": ["payment:topup", "payment:withdraw"]
}
```

## Registrasi Plugin

- Manifest loader: hanya di `pluginLoader.ts` via `MANIFEST_LOADERS`. Metro butuh static import path.
- Jangan hardcode daftar plugin di tempat lain; pakai `PluginRegistry.getEnabledPlugins()`, `getEnabledRoutes()`, `getRouteByName()`.

## Core vs Enabled

- `type === 'core-plugin'` otomatis diload.
- Plugin lain di-load jika ada di `config.enabledModules` (app config).

## Validasi

- Pakai `validateManifestOrThrow` dari `@core/config` sebelum register; manifest harus lolos `manifestValidator`.
